267
00:25:48,480 --> 00:25:50,994
I want people to enjoy their work.

268
00:25:52,560 --> 00:25:56,109
Just last week I had to let a girl go.
Very beautiful, too.

269
00:25:56,280 --> 00:25:59,511
But she was too vulgar.
It’s a shame.

270
00:26:00,480 --> 00:26:01,959
Come sit down.

271
00:26:05,400 --> 00:26:09,234
What’s your name?
