275
00:26:18,600 --> 00:26:21,114
- No, thank you.
- I insist.

276
00:26:21,240 --> 00:26:23,470
Cherries in brandy.

277
00:26:23,840 --> 00:26:28,072
We need to find you a name —
something simple and smart,

278
00:26:28,200 --> 00:26:30,714
and easy to remember.

279
00:26:30,840 --> 00:26:33,195
We can think of one together,
if you like.

280
00:26:41,600 --> 00:26:43,591
