311
00:28:44,600 --> 00:28:47,034
Get acquainted.
I’ll be right back.

312
00:28:49,760 --> 00:28:51,079
Pallas!

313
00:28:51,240 --> 00:28:54,312
A hell of a woman, from head to toe.

314
00:28:54,440 --> 00:28:56,431
