321
00:29:12,400 --> 00:29:15,312
Very refined.
Just how I like ’em.

322
00:29:15,480 --> 00:29:19,029
You promised me a present.
I’d love a dress like that.

323
00:29:19,160 --> 00:29:21,276
I’m not Rothschild, baby!

324
00:29:21,400 --> 00:29:22,879
Too bad.

325
00:29:23,920 --> 00:29:25,751
What a great cut!

326
00:29:26,920 --> 00:29:28,672
The detail work is incredible.

327
00:29:28,800 --> 00:29:31,314
It’s easy to dress well
when you’ve got money.

328
00:29:31,440 --> 00:29:33,476
But you can’t buy class.

329
00:29:33,600 --> 00:29:35,591
Here’s the champagne.

330
00:29:36,600 --> 00:29:38,591
My throat was feeling dry.

331
