so don’t get upset.

363
00:31:59,520 --> 00:32:02,239
Do what he wants.
That’s all he asks.

364
00:32:02,440 --> 00:32:04,476
- No, I want to go.
- What?

365
00:32:05,120 --> 00:32:08,954
You about done putting on airs?
Where do you think you are?

366
00:32:09,080 --> 00:32:10,559
Go on.

367
00:32:11,760 --> 00:32:14,718
Yes, ma’am. I’m going.

368
00:32:14,840 --> 00:32:16,876
Leave me alone, you two.

369
00:32:17,280 --> 00:32:19,840
Seems you need a firm hand, eh?

370
00:32:27,840 --> 00:32:29,319
Go on.

371
00:32:32,720 --> 00:32:34,119
Hi there.

372
00:32:34,800 --> 00:32:36,392
Close the door.

373
00:32:38,560 --> 00:32:40,039
Come here.

374
00:32:40,760 --> 00:32:44,594
