390
00:33:42,640 --> 00:33:44,073
There.

391
00:33:44,400 --> 00:33:45,833
See?

392
00:33:46,640 --> 00:33:48,312
That’s more like it.

393
00:33:51,160 --> 00:33:52,593
So...

394
00:33:52,720 --> 00:33:55,188
you need the rough stuff, do you?

395
00:34:01,080 --> 00:34:03,719
Jack of clubs, my gin card.

396
00:34:08,520 --> 00:34:10,670
