is sure taking a long time.

397
00:34:10,800 --> 00:34:12,313
He always does.

398
00:34:15,680 --> 00:34:17,033
Gin.

399
00:35:50,640 --> 00:35:53,791
Séverine, where are you?
Are you ready?

400
00:35:56,320 --> 00:35:58,038
You’re in here?

401
00:35:58,160 --> 00:36:00,720
What’s the matter?
Is something wrong?

402
00:36:02,560 --> 00:36:04,278
Are you ill?

403
00:36:08,720 --> 00:36:10,711
You don’t have a temperature.

404
00:36:11,480 --> 00:36:14,392
Shall I send for someone?
- No, it’s nothing.

405
00:36:14,520 --> 00:36:16,112
l was sleeping.

406
00:36:16,240 --> 00:36:18,595
I had a headache.
I don’t know why.

407
00:36:19,040 --> 00:36:21,838
I took an aspirin and a hot bath.
l’ll feel better tomorrow.

408
00:36:21,960 --> 00:36:23,598
What time is it?

409
00:36:23,720 --> 00:36:25,153
lt’s late.

410
00:36:25,280 --> 00:36:27,635
I’ll call the Févrets to cancel.

411
00:36:27,760 --> 00:36:30,035
- You go by yourself.
- Absolutely not.

412
00:36:30,160 --> 00:36:33,789
I’ll be much better here.
Anyway, I have work to do.

413
00:36:35,400 --> 00:36:37,391
Get some rest. Good night.

414
00:37:06,320 --> 00:37:08,038
/s the soup ready?

415
00:37:11,280 --> 00:37:14,192
