you have to be serious about it.

443
00:38:46,720 --> 00:38:47,755
Yes.

444
00:38:47,880 --> 00:38:49,916
Can I count on you every day?

445
00:38:50,040 --> 00:38:52,156
Yes, but only until 5:00.

446
00:38:52,720 --> 00:38:54,039
Go on in.

447
00:38:56,840 --> 00:38:59,513
Hello, madame.
Nice to see you again.

448
00:39:00,280 --> 00:39:02,191
lt’s Belle de jour.
How are you?

449
00:39:02,360 --> 00:39:04,555
- Fine, thanks.
- You ran out on us.

450
00:39:04,680 --> 00:39:07,114
- Why didn’t you come back sooner?
- I couldn’t.

451
00:39:07,280 --> 00:39:09,589
- Give me your coat.
- Thank you.

452
00:39:09,720 --> 00:39:13,713
It’s so nice.
Say, may I ask a favor?

453
00:39:13,840 --> 00:39:17,515
Could I borrow it this Sunday?
I’ll bring it back Monday.

454
00:39:17,640 --> 00:39:20,234
Listen, I hate to say no,

455
00:39:20,360 --> 00:39:23,670
but Sunday wouldn’t work so well,
because —

456
00:39:23,840 --> 00:39:25,831
