457
00:39:25,960 --> 00:39:28,952
Carducci! Only the best, eh?

458
00:39:29,760 --> 00:39:31,398
Who are you?

459
00:39:33,480 --> 00:39:35,835
Was it tough coming back?

460
00:39:36,200 --> 00:39:37,713
I do this because of my fiancé.

461
00:39:37,880 --> 00:39:40,997
He was hurt in a cycling accident
and can’t work.

462
00:39:41,120 --> 00:39:44,510
