Get dressed!

482
00:42:12,360 --> 00:42:13,793
Come in.

483
00:42:20,000 --> 00:42:21,877
The marquise called?

484
00:42:22,120 --> 00:42:23,439
Yes.

485
00:42:26,680 --> 00:42:29,069
