500
00:43:47,960 --> 00:43:50,428
- The marquise called?
- Yes, Victor.

501
00:43:50,560 --> 00:43:52,949
lsn’t her ladyship satisfied
with my services?

502
00:43:53,080 --> 00:43:55,469
You’re always making mistakes.

503
00:43:56,320 --> 00:43:59,039
It’s true, I admit it.

504
00:43:59,960 --> 00:44:01,951
But the marquise is so good,

505
00:44:02,160 --> 00:44:04,674
so kind,
and especially so beautiful.

506
00:44:04,800 --> 00:44:06,313
lnsolent man!

507
00:44:09,160 --> 00:44:10,559
Look here.

508
00:44:11,000 --> 00:44:13,468
Are you blind? Can’t you see?

509
00:44:13,640 --> 00:44:15,471
There’s dust everywhere.

510
00:44:15,640 --> 00:44:18,393
There, there, and there!

