808
01:09:52,080 --> 01:09:54,196
I’m telling you, I’m not bored.

809
01:09:54,360 --> 01:09:56,430
We can stay another week
if you’d like.

810
01:09:56,560 --> 01:10:00,348
No, we’ll leave tomorrow.
I have to get back anyway.

811
01:10:16,280 --> 01:10:17,838
See you.

812
01:10:19,000 --> 01:10:20,319
Something wrong, Mr. Marcel?

813
